Baduki

BA: word/syllable/sound
DU: collection
KI: the

Baduki is the language of the Kekelpliths

---------------------------------

Kekelplithf

ĒK : two
EL : blade
PLITHF : rizen

---------------------------------

Brekkelēga

BREK : martial
KEL : blade
Ē : feeling/awareness
GA : move

ĒGA : dance

The Brekkelēga dance utilizes the Kekelplithfs' finblades as weapons.

---------------------------------

Syllables:

UF	: zero / none / nothing / air
OT	: one
ĒK      : two
UR	: three
ART	: four
OZ	: five
ZIK	: six
UZU	: seven
ZAT	: eight

ĒK-ART 	: 42 <[34]
UR-ĒK 	: 23 <[19]
UZU-ĒK	: 27 <[23]
ĒK-OZ	: 52 <[42]

